NEED AN EVENT SPACE? BE OUR GUEST.
Our upstairs deck and bar are available to rent for your special catered event.
For rates and information contact us at:
info@barnhills.com
Barnhill's is located in the center of Flagler Beach at 202 South Central Ave., next to The Gallery of Local Art (GOLA).  We have great views of the ocean and Flagler Beach special events (First Friday Entertainment, Fireworks, Parades, etc.).
Barnhill's is honored to provide a beautiful space for ANY event.
